comments: George (LAC) brings his forearm towards Curry's (GSW) front and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Harden (LAC) and Podziemski (GSW) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.
George (LAC) moves forward with his right arm brought toward Curry's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs with Curry's side/front as they each approach the screen.
Podziemski (GSW) is extending slightly prior to marginal side-to-side contact occurring with George (LAC) as the screen is set.
Curry (GSW) establishes his left foot as his pivot and slides it before releasing his dribble.

George (LAC) is moving forward towards Curry (GSW), and George then brings his left arm toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with Curry's shoulder/neck area. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Theis (LAC) brushes Curry's (GSW) right forearm and marginal contact occurs as Curry changes direction after his gather. Theis then cleanly blocks Curry's driving shot attempt.
Harden's (LAC) left arm comes forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Podziemski's (GSW) front after Podziemski has already started to lose his balance during the rebound.

Replay review of the out of bounds call pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Harden (LAC) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Warriors.
Curry's (GSW) hands come forward as he establishes himself in Mann's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs with Mann's side as Mann moves over the screen.
George (LAC) and Podziemski (GSW) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.
Thompson (GSW) has a grasp of Leonard's (LAC) slightly extended off-arm and marginal contact occurs as Leonard drives inside the perimeter.
Thompson (GSW) does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that the foul by George (LAC) on Moody (GSW) met the criteria for a clear path foul.
Mann (LAC) brings his right hand toward Curry's (GSW) side and marginal contact occurs at the end of Curry's drive.
Moody (GSW) is moving forward as he pursues the rebound and marginal body contact occurs with Leonard (LAC) as Leonard retrieves the ball in the air.
Mann (LAC) and Moody (GSW) mutually engage and disengage with one another as they move into the lane following the expiration of the screen.
Harden (LAC) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Moody (GSW) and is not in a legal guarding position when he initiates body contact with Moody in the lane.
Thompson (GSW) places his hand momentarily on George's (LAC) side before correcting.
Thompson (GSW) brushes George's (LAC) left arm/side and marginal contact occurs as George releases the pass.
Powell (LAC) and Podziemski (GSW) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Mann (LAC) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Curry's (GSW) slightly extended off-arm as Curry releases away from Mann at the end of the drive.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) brings his hands forward toward Curry's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs with Curry's front as he drives inside the perimeter.
Westbrook (LAC) legally contests Green's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
